      desc: Instead of sleeping you meditate deeply, remaining semi-conscious, for
        4 hours a day. While meditating, you dream after a fashion; such dreams are
        actually mental exercises that have become reflexive after years of practice.
        After resting in this way, you gain the same benefit a human would from 8
        hours of sleep.
