    features:
    - featName: Adrenaline
      desc: "You can fight where other warriors would fail. You can spend one AP
        to regain Vitality points equal to 1d6 + your Body modifier.<br> You can
        make this action a number of times equal to your Talent. One hour of rest
        replenishes one use of Adrenaline.<br> At 6th general level your Adrenaline\u2019s
        healing die changes from 1d6 to 1d8."
