      types:
      - Utility
      range: Self
      APCost: 1
      isReaction: 0
      staminaCost: 0
      desc: A flame appears in your hand. The flame remains there for the duration
        and harms neither you nor your equipment. The spell ends if you dismiss it
        with 1 AP or if you cast it again.<br> Anyone else touching the flame take
        2 + Spellforce magical fire damage.
