    - manName: Hurl Flame
      types:
      - Combat
      - Projectile
      range: 6m
      APCost: 1
      isReaction: 0
      staminaCost: 3
      desc: When having summoned a flame, you can throw it at any target within your
        range. You make an Spellcraft check. That attack deals half the damage when
        blocked, and it can be dodged as normal.<br> If the attack hits, target takes
        4 + Spellforce magical fire damage.
      rollHit:
